          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "There remains a debate about whether Biden and congressional Democrats’ recent promises of $2,000 checks were always taking into account the $600 checks in the COVID-relief bill passed by Congress last month.",
